readable.content: A man and a boy watch a dog leap to catch a ball . A man and a child are standing near a dog who is jumping . A man and a small boy watch their small , white dog catch a toy in the air . A small black brown and white dog catches a football in midair as a man and child look on . Small white dog with spot on back leaping in air with football in mouth with small boy and man watching .
